{"type":"message","id":"8b953760","parentId":"4800b4d4","timestamp":"2026-04-03T08:19:17.118Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"没问题，我已经把这条规则刻进骨子里了：\n\n1. 更新了 `AGENTS.md` 的 **Red Lines**，明确以后安装任何 skill 都必须先通过 `skill-vetter` 审核。\n2. 在 `MEMORY.md` 和今天的记忆文件里记录了这项安全偏好。\n\n以后只要你让我装 skill，我会先运行审核流程。还有其他建议吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":1855,"output":88,"cacheRead":16150,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18093,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775204355018,"responseId":"chatcmpl-e1bdcb99-b623-4418-a7c3-c0821a36c371"}}
