{"type":"message","id":"73f3aca4","parentId":"1bdbdf22","timestamp":"2026-04-03T08:25:54.570Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"已经安装并配置好啦。\n\n虽然 QMD 官方推荐用 `bun`，但它本质上是一个 Node.js 驱动的包，发布在 NPM 上。既然你的系统里已经有 `node` 和 `npm`，我就直接通过 `npm install -g @tobilu/qmd` 完成了安装。\n\n**我刚才做的操作：**\n1. **安装 QMD**：通过 `npm` 全局安装。\n2. **修改配置**：在你的 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 中把 `memory.backend` 设置为了 `qmd`。\n3. **重启网关**：运行了 `openclaw gateway restart` 让新配置生效。\n\n等网关重启完成，OpenClaw 就会自动管理 QMD 并在后台下载必要的 GGUF 模型。你可以稍后运行 `openclaw memory status` 看看 QMD 是否已经成功接管了内存索引。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3-flash","usage":{"input":3345,"output":202,"cacheRead":24166,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27713,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775204751193,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b096f546-2324-4e09-a642-1fd8d45c6e9a"}}
